      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study performed (2.1M, 5.8M, 14.2M elements). GCI for NIH ranges from 2.1% to 4.7% across operating points. Asymptotic range of convergence confirmed (GCI ratio 1.02–1.08). Medium mesh selected for production runs."
