      "rationale": "Validation performed on FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry identical to COU device geometry. Operating range (2.5–7.5 L/min, 2000–3500 RPM) encompasses CPB clinical range (4–6 L/min). Bovine blood analog accepted surrogate per ISO 10993-4 precedent. Validation relevance assessed as high for MRL 2."
